        href="https://support.microsoft.com/eres-eres/help/17442/windows-internet-explorer-delete-manage-cookies#ie=ie-10"
        rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
        https://support.microsoft.com/eres-eres/help/17442/windows-internet-explorer-delete-manage-cookies#ie=ie-10</a>)
    </p>
